name: "Fallen Angel" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing over photograph of a cherubic bust.] I spotted this evil little figure stuck to the side of a building in Lincoln City, Oregon, (USA), and snapped a digital photo with my phone. Then, using a no-longer-supported free app on my phone, I drew over the image and added funky colors. NOW, it looks just like the creature that was floating over my bed at 3:AM a few nights ago! Aaaaaahhhhh!!! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
